Fragemetns:
Used to reuseable component
Every view have one controller is avaiable, in fragement no controller available we can use it as same controller of the view for actions.
Fragement file extension should: <file name>.fragement.xml , this file should be available under the webcontent folder.

fragement.xml: view
compulsory follow with first tag
<core:fragementDefinition .... >
.....
.....
</core:fragementDefinition>

for I18N:
save filename with <fielname>.properties
Ex:webapp/i18n/i18n.properties (New)

showHelloButtonText=Say Hello
helloMsg=Hello {0}

For multltiple languages
for example i18n_de.properties for German, i18n_en.properties for English, 
